data.description: Come home to this meticulously renovated 3-bedroom 3-bath ranch nestled in a tranquil neighborhood in the heart of the Pocono Mountains. The new modern kitchen with breakfast counter and skylight is a dream to cook in and opens up seamlessly to the dining room and adjacent living room, all with brand new flooring creating a harmonious blend of style and functionality. Two completely refinished full baths and 3 bedrooms round out the main floor. The 1500 sq ft. fully finished basement with kitchenette and full bath is ideal for in-laws, teens, and kids of any age.  Bilco doors allow easy access to the fenced in backyard where laughter and memories await.  Walking distance to the community lake and pool.  This is not just a house; it's a canvas for the life you've always dreamed of.
